#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:86
msgid ""
"The default theme now only uses named colors, so it will track the "
"terminal's palette (:issue:`9913`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:87
msgid ""
"The Dracula theme has now been synced with upstream (:issue:`9807`); use "
"``fish_config`` to re-apply it to pick up the changes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:88
msgid "``fish_vcs_prompt`` now also supports fossil (:issue:`9497`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:89
msgid ""
"Prompts which display the working directory using the ``prompt_pwd`` "
"function correctly display directories beginning with dashes (:issue:"
"`10169`)."
msgstr ""

