#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:470
msgid ""
"``status fish-path`` on Linux-based platforms could print the path with a "
"\" (deleted)\" suffix (such as ``/usr/bin/fish (deleted)``), which is now "
"removed (:issue:`9019`)."
