#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:2629
msgid ""
"Apple macOS Sierra 10.12.5 introduced a problem with launching web browsers "
"from other programs using AppleScript. This affects the fish Web "
"configuration (``fish_config``); users on these platforms will need to "
"manually open the address displayed in the terminal, such as by copying and "
"pasting it into a browser. This problem will be fixed with macOS 10.12.6."
