#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3152
msgid ""
"A new ``string`` builtin to handle… strings! This builtin will measure, "
"split, search and replace text strings, including using regular expressions. "
"It can also be used to turn lists into plain strings using ``join``. "
"``string`` can be used in place of ``sed``, ``grep``, ``tr``, ``cut``, and "
"``awk`` in many situations. (:issue:`2296`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3157
msgid ""
"Allow using escape as the Meta modifier key, by waiting after seeing an "
"escape character wait up to 300ms for an additional character. This is "
"consistent with readline (e.g. bash) and can be configured via the "
"``fish_escape_delay_ms variable``. This allows using escape as the Meta "
"modifier. (:issue:`1356`)"
msgstr ""

