"read (:issue:`1698`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3336
msgid ""
"``type`` has a new ``-q`` option to suppress output (:issue:`1540` and, like "
"other shells, ``type -a`` now prints all matches for a command (:issue:"
"`261`)."
