"other shells (:issue:`89`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3348
msgid ""
"The ``SHLVL`` environment variable is incremented correctly (:issue:`1634` "
"& :issue:`1693`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3350
msgid ""
"Added completions for ``adb`` (:issue:`1165` & :issue:`1211`), ``apt`` (:"
"issue:`2018`), ``aura`` (:issue:`1292`), ``composer`` (:issue:`1607`), "
"``cygport`` (:issue:`1841`), ``dropbox`` (:issue:`1533`), ``elixir`` (:issue:"
"`1167`), ``fossil``, ``heroku`` (:issue:`1790`), ``iex`` (:issue:`1167`), "
"``kitchen`` (:issue:`2000`), ``nix`` (:issue:`1167`), ``node``/``npm`` (:"
"issue:`1566`), ``opam`` (:issue:`1615`), ``setfacl`` (:issue:`1752`), "
